help physical
Nymphs are the embodiment of beauty itself. Nymphs appear similar
to female elves with extraordinary beauty and charm. They are fleet
of foot and can be very clever. Nymphs skin tone and hair and eyes vary
greatly but always fall in a combination pleasing to the eye.
end help

help racial
The nymphs of Primal Darkness search for simpler times. They despise
war and suffering and wish only to live among their male followers
which serve and protect the nymph. However, in this age, conflict is a
fact of life and even the beautiful nymph must resort to crafty
measures in order to survive.
end help
